---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /
isHome: true
---

{% set featured = collections.posts[0] %}

<div class="editorial-shell">
  <section class="editorial-hero page" aria-labelledby="cover-title">
    <div class="cover-folio" aria-label="博客信息">
      <span>个人博客 · 持续更新</span>
      <span>始于 {{ site.year }}</span>
    </div>

    <div class="cover-grid">
      <h1 id="cover-title">
        先<em>想明白</em>，<br />
        再写清楚。
      </h1>
      <div class="cover-deck">
        <p>记录开发、设计，以及那些需要时间才能想明白的问题。</p>
        <span>{{ site.name }} 写作与维护</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <figure class="cover-visual">
      <div class="cover-image-reveal">
        <img
          src="/assets/img/editorial-hero.webp"
          alt="窗边工作台上的空白笔记本、铅笔与图纸"
          width="1799"
          height="874"
          loading="eager"
          fetchpriority="high"
        />
      </div>
      <figcaption>
        <span>关于清晰、克制与动手实践</span>
        <span>文章与短记 · {{ currentYear }}</span>
      </figcaption>
    </figure>
  </section>

  {% if featured %}
    <section class="feature-section page" aria-labelledby="feature-title">
      <div class="section-index" aria-hidden="true">01</div>
      <article class="feature-story">
        <div class="feature-meta">
          <span>本期首选</span>
          <span>{{ featured.data.category }} · {{ featured.date | readableDate }}</span>
          <span>{{ featured.templateContent | readingTime }} 分钟阅读</span>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-copy">
          <h2 id="feature-title">
            <a href="{{ featured.url }}">{{ featured.data.title }}</a>
          </h2>
          <p>{{ featured.data.description }}</p>
          <a class="text-link" href="{{ featured.url }}">阅读全文 <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span></a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>
  {% endif %}

  <section class="latest-section page" aria-labelledby="latest-title">
    <header class="section-heading">
      <div>
        <span class="section-index" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
        <h2 id="latest-title">近期文章</h2>
      </div>
      <a class="text-link" href="/archive/">查看全部文章 <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span></a>
    </header>

    <ol class="story-list">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
        <li>
          <a class="story-row" href="{{ post.url }}">
            <span class="story-number">{{ loop.index | padNum(2) }}</span>
            <span class="story-main">
              <span class="story-category">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
              <strong>{{ post.data.title }}</strong>
              <span class="story-description">{{ post.data.description }}</span>
            </span>
            <span class="story-date">
              {{ post.date | shortDate }}
              <i aria-hidden="true">↗</i>
            </span>
          </a>
        </li>
      {% else %}
        <li class="empty-state">文章正在整理中。</li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="notes-editorial page" aria-labelledby="notes-title">
    <header class="section-heading">
      <div>
        <span class="section-index" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
        <h2 id="notes-title">短记</h2>
      </div>
      <p>一些还没写成文章、但值得先记下的判断。</p>
    </header>

    <ol class="note-grid">
      {% for note in collections.notes %}
        <li>
          <a class="note-card" href="/notes/#note-{{ note.data.number }}">
            <div class="note-card__meta">
              <span>{{ note.data.number or (loop.index | padNum(3)) }}</span>
              <time datetime="{{ note.date | htmlDate }}">{{ note.date | shortDate }}</time>
            </div>
            <h3>{{ note.data.title }}</h3>
            <p>{{ note.data.description }}</p>
          </a>
        </li>
      {% else %}
        <li class="empty-state">短记正在整理中。</li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="directions-section page" aria-labelledby="directions-title">
    <header class="section-heading">
      <div>
        <span class="section-index" aria-hidden="true">04</span>
        <h2 id="directions-title">三个方向</h2>
      </div>
      <p>不追每个变化，只记录那些值得反复回看的问题。</p>
    </header>

    <div class="direction-grid">
      {% for direction in directions %}
        {% set posts = collections.posts | filterByCategory(direction.key) %}
        <a class="direction-item" href="/{{ direction.slug }}/">
          <span class="direction-count">{{ posts.length | padNum(2) }} 篇</span>
          <h3>{{ direction.key }}<i>{{ direction.en }}</i></h3>
          <p>{{ direction.description }}</p>
          <span class="direction-action">浏览主题 <i aria-hidden="true">↗</i></span>
        </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-editorial page" id="about" aria-labelledby="about-title">
    <div class="about-aside">
      <span class="section-index" aria-hidden="true">05</span>
      <span>关于本站</span>
    </div>
    <div class="about-content">
      <h2 id="about-title">“写作不只是交付结论，<em>也在记录判断如何形成。</em>”</h2>
      <div class="about-body">
        <p>这里收录我对系统、智能与界面的长期观察。文章可以持续生长，旧判断也允许被新的理解修正。</p>
        <p>我更关心：一个问题为什么值得提出，以及它如何在实践中变得清晰。</p>
      </div>
      <a class="editorial-button" href="{{ site.github }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        在 GitHub 找到我 <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
